"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"US President Donald Trump has called for regime change in Iran and said major combat operations are under way. Iran has retaliated with a missile barrage towards Israel, while explosions have been heard in Qatar, Bahrain, Saudi Arabia, and the UAE.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump Calls for Regime Change\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU., Donald Trump, ha pedido un cambio de gobierno en Ir\u00e1n y dijo que hay operaciones de combate importantes en marcha. Ir\u00e1n ha respondido con misiles hacia Israel, mientras se escucharon explosiones en Qatar, Bahr\u00e9in, Arabia Saudita y los Emiratos \u00c1rabes Unidos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump Calls for Regime Change\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The two countries are repairing a strained relationship as they also seek to reduce their trade reliance on the US.\",            \"english_title\": \"Countries Repair Relationship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los dos pa\u00edses est\u00e1n arreglando una relaci\u00f3n dif\u00edcil mientras buscan reducir su dependencia comercial de EE.UU.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Countries Repair Relationship\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Dozens of well-known groups faced shutdown under a new Israeli law, although the reprieve might be temporary.\",            \"english_title\": \"Groups Face Shutdown\",            \"translated_version\": \"Docenas de grupos conocidos enfrentan cierre bajo una nueva ley israel\u00ed, aunque el respiro podr\u00eda ser temporal.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Groups Face Shutdown\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police fire tear gas to disperse crowds allegedly trying to take banknotes from the crash site.\",            \"english_title\": \"Police Use Tear Gas\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda usa gas lacrim\u00f3geno para dispersar a multitudes que supuestamente intentan tomar billetes del lugar del accidente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Police Use Tear Gas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The latest attacks by Pakistan follow months of clashes between the two countries, despite agreeing to a fragile ceasefire in October.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pakistan Attacks Again\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los \u00faltimos ataques de Pakist\u00e1n siguen meses de enfrentamientos entre los dos pa\u00edses, a pesar de acordar un fr\u00e1gil alto el fuego en octubre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pakistan Attacks Again\"        }    ]}"